
================
 Rule Structure
================



--------------
 Common Rules
--------------

---+~~~~~~~~~~~~~
000:bad\s+stuff.*

- Rule ID  : 3 digit identificator
+ Separator: 1 character separator
~ Rule Re  : N characters of rule regular expression



-------------
 Other rules
-------------

-----+~~~~~~~~~~~~~
00000:bad\s+stuff.*

- Rule ID  : 5 digit identificator
+ Separator: 1 character separator
~ Rule Re  : N characters of rule regular expression
